description:
Let's make a map! The goal of this series is to build a PvP arena of sorts, that is capable of a few specific technical functions needed for my game. This series will likely focus on the designing and technical aspects of the map instead of the aesthetics.

We have begun building the actual map! My main goal now is to get the layout of everything figured out and how all the pieces will interact with each other.
